snippet.title: Friday Night Funkin' - V.S. Garcello FULL WEEK - Smoke 'Em Out Struggle [FNF Mods | Very Hard]
snippet.description:
Friday Night Funkin' Smoke 'Em Out Struggle version 1update vs Garcello (FULL WEEK) for the PC in 1080p Ultra HD. This mod is best experienced on HARD mode so we'll be playing it in that mode.

FNF Smoke 'Em Out Struggle 1.0 version is the newest update featuring Garcello along with new cutscenes. We'll be playing the full week of Smoke 'Em Out Struggle Week in the hardest difficulty. It's up to Boyfriend to save his girlfriend and himself with the power of music!

All Songs from Smoke 'Em Out Struggle Full Week  Mod Timestamp
00:00 Intro
00:06 Dialogue 1
00:57 HEADACHE (Garcello Vs Boyfriend)
02:50 Dialogue 2
03:25 NERVES (Garcello Vs Boyfriend)
05:26 Garcello Death
05:38 Dialogue 3
06:15 RELEASE (Garcello Vs Boyfriend)
08:43 Dialogue 4
09:23 Fading - Final Fareware Song
10:12 Garcello Ending
